Riverbed® Stingray™ Traffic Manager 9.0  is a full performance software and virtual Layer 7 application delivery controller (ADC) that enables enterprises and cloud operators to create, manage, and deliver key services more quickly, more flexibly, and at a lower cost. Stingray Traffic Manager 9.0 offers much more than just load balancing. It controls and optimizes end-user services by inspecting, transforming, prioritizing, and routing application traffic. The powerful TrafficScript™ engine facilitates the implementation of traffic management policies that are unique to an application by allowing organizations to build custom functionality or leverage existing features in Stingray Traffic Manager in a specialized way. 